N2  - We counter Barney's challenges and reaffirm the tautology of the elemental business-level resource-based ?view? (RBV). We develop a mathematical representation of the RBV as a first step toward formalizing its statements. We then explore the implications of our assertion (and Barney's agreement) that resource value is indeed determined outside of the RBV.
AB  - We counter Barney's challenges and reaffirm the tautology of the elemental business-level resource-based ?view? (RBV). We develop a mathematical representation of the RBV as a first step toward formalizing its statements. We then explore the implications of our assertion (and Barney's agreement) that resource value is indeed determined outside of the RBV.
